      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 0,
      "text": "Mhm. Good morning. Welcome Towers."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 6.37,
      "start_time": 4.48,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 1,
      "text": "Good morning. Is David available?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 7.94,
      "start_time": 6.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 2,
      "text": "May I ask who's calling?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 10.05,
      "start_time": 8.74,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "This is Andy Keith calling"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 10.11,
      "start_time": 10.05,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 11.12,
      "start_time": 10.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "with rentable,"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 31.32,
      "start_time": 12.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "Andy keith. Okay, just a moment. Hello?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 34.52,
      "start_time": 32.24,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "David? Good morning. And how are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 37.03,
      "start_time": 35.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "Hi, how are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 40.32,
      "start_time": 37.44,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "I'm good. Hey, is it alright if I steal them in it,"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 45.45,
      "start_time": 42.71,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "Ah Andy, where are you calling from?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 54.48,
      "start_time": 46.15,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "calling from rentable, I was following up some emails I sent you earlier this week. Um I've had email communications with you over the years as well year."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 69.2,
      "start_time": 53.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "Oh yeah, I think I recall seeing an email like that. Uh Andy we don't need to go on with that. We're we have our own site here and we're occupancy is great. There's nothing else we need to do at this time."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 89.88,
      "start_time": 70.48,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Alright. Um I mean even sometime I'd love to buy a coffee and just share what we do just so you know when it's appropriate because I've never sat down with you doesn't even mean it has to be now, but just to get to know you you and your business um because there might be a need some day, I mean would that be would you be open to that?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 104.16,
      "start_time": 91.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Well um Andy not at this time. Um you know, if you wanna send me an email, I'll keep it in mind. Um but you know, again we just don't need to do anything at this time and we haven't for quite a while,"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 106.73,
      "start_time": 104.85,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "Okay, and do you guys"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 108.54,
      "start_time": 106.74,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "can I just ask you use any vendors currently,"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 114.32,
      "start_time": 112.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "any Avengers for what"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 127.94,
      "start_time": 115.31,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "you know, internet listing sites, leveraging, social media, um reducing operating costs. I don't know. Just to drive occupancy. I mean I guess you don't need to drive occupancy, but do you list anywhere outside of your website,"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 136.16,
      "start_time": 130.2,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "we do. Uh We do have apartments dot com as as well."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 140.9,
      "start_time": 138.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "Is that the main source that you guys use? Like probably the only one"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 148.28,
      "start_time": 142.4,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Yeah and again it works very uh well for us handy"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 168.97,
      "start_time": 149.18,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "cool. I never get time with you. So I had to ask a couple questions. Um well when can I buy a coffee, when would it be appropriate? Just to kind of uh pick your brain share what we do, we don't have a one size fits all solution. So sending an email is just gonna end up in the trash bin anyways? Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 176.75,
      "start_time": 169.75,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "you're probably right but we don't need to sit down and have coffee Andy. Um You know again it's just"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 176.88,
      "start_time": 176.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 24,
      "text": "you like"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 177.13,
      "start_time": 176.75,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "not"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 177.42,
      "start_time": 176.88,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 26,
      "text": "food?"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 178.88,
      "start_time": 177.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 27,
      "text": "interested in,"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 182.63,
      "start_time": 180.02,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "Well yeah you you won't be interested in what you don't know."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 186.41,
      "start_time": 183.51,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "you know, perhaps it's not necessary."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 188.88,
      "start_time": 188.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 189.2,
      "start_time": 188.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 31,
      "text": "Hm."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 190.62,
      "start_time": 188.88,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 32,
      "text": "I feel it man. I'm not gonna push you anymore."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 191.5,
      "start_time": 191.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 33,
      "text": "Okay well"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 192.03,
      "start_time": 191.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 34,
      "text": "Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 192.87,
      "start_time": 191.5,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7b7659ea-c85b-4c4e-9d4b-e875641fca6b",
      "order_number": 35,
      "text": "thanks for calling."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
      "recording_id": "6f9aa807-c510-43a8-84d7-c627ad087d8e",
      "end_time": 198.24,
      "start_time": 192.39,
      "recording_attendee_id": "02da1e48-5798-42bf-99c5-9efe81db73a9",
      "order_number": 36,
      "text": "I hope you have a great holiday. And if you do think of me sometime, drop me a line."
    },
    {
      "id": "f6f5a3c4-c311-470d-8442-f177d37dc0ef",
